rows.label: qev055403_MSG0001
rows.name: How fares the search for senirapa water?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055403_MSG0002
rows.name: Kon'luarb has taught us much about the Orphe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055403_MSG0003
rows.name:
But it is a...strange sensation.
Each new thing we learn feels at once familiar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev055403_MSG0004
rows.name:
It is as if we are merely remembering what we have
forgotten. I suppose that is the way of us Orpheans,
and the workings of the Ovah.[ST:wait ]
